thread.title: Erica Martin

author: Erica Martin
title: Erica Martin
text: I like the website. I only shopped the bathing suit section, and was initially overwhelmed by the sheer volume of items. The website, however, does a good job of dividing the section by subcategories, which made it much easier to shop. Overall. I feel like I picked some really nice pieces. I'm looking forward to seeing if the images online match what I receive in person.
